# Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs)

This folder contains examples of SOPs and workflow guides I created or adapted to improve consistency and compliance across teams.  
All content has been **anonymized or recreated with sample data**.

## Files
- **onboarding-checklist.docx** – Step-by-step checklist for onboarding new employees.  
- **invoice-approval-workflow.pdf** – Flowchart outlining procurement and invoice processing.  
- **inventory-reconciliation-sop.docx** – Process guide for monthly stock audits.

## Highlights
- Ensures consistent application of policies.  
- Reduces errors and improves audit readiness.  
- Helps new staff quickly adapt to procedures.
